name: Junedog.finance
description: Junedog.finance is the home of a community-based meme token with symbol JUNE. The smart contract rewards one recipient periodically based on recent transactions. The community can initiate the picking of the lucky winner once there are enough entries, and the minimum amount has been reached. It is a place to crypto responsibly while having fun. The community alongside Junedog.finance will be growing and bringing focus to new memes, cryptocurrency utilities, and decentralized apps. This is what sets Junedog.finance apart from other ETH tokens.
